import React from 'react';

import {
    Container,
    ContainerHeader,
    ContainerBody,
    ContainerListCalls,
    Image,
    ContainerTitle,
    Title,
    ContainerBox,
    TitleMessage,
    Box,
    ButtonFilder
} from './styles'

import { Profile } from '../../components/Profile'
import { ListCallsCategory } from '../../components/CategoryLists/ListCallsCategory'
import filter from '../../assets/Icons/filter.png'
import { CustomSwitch } from '../../components/Customs/CustomSwitch'

import { useNavigation, ParamListBase } from "@react-navigation/native"
import { DrawerNavigationProp } from "@react-navigation/drawer";

export function Mentor() {

    const navigation = useNavigation<DrawerNavigationProp<ParamListBase>>()

    return (
        <Container>

            <ContainerHeader>
                <Profile
                    onPress={() => navigation.openDrawer()}
                    date='Terça, 11 de maio'
                    hellow='Olá,'
                    strong='Nome do mentor' />
                {/* <Header /> */}
            </ContainerHeader>

            <ContainerBox>
                <Box>
                    <TitleMessage>Está disponível para atendimento?</TitleMessage>
                    <CustomSwitch />
                </Box>
            </ContainerBox>


            <ContainerBody>
                <ContainerListCalls>
                    <ContainerTitle>
                        <Title>Seus chamados</Title>
                        <ButtonFilder onPress={() => alert('em desenvolvimento...')}>
                            <Image source={filter} />
                        </ButtonFilder>
                    </ContainerTitle>
                    <ListCallsCategory
                        name="Eduardo Cunha"
                        message="Este chamado foi encerrado"
                        date="Hoje"
                        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Chat')} />
                </ContainerListCalls>

            </ContainerBody>

        </Container>
    )
}
